title: Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate

heading_context: Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate
chunks.html_content:
You can get a replacement MOT certificate online if you’ve lost or damaged the original.

This service is free.
chunks.plain_content:
Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate
You can get a replacement MOT certificate online if you’ve lost or damaged the original.
This service is free.

heading_context: Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate
chunks.html_content: There’s a different service to get a replacement MOT certificate for vehicles tested in Northern Ireland.
chunks.plain_content:
Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate
There’s a different service to get a replacement MOT certificate for vehicles tested in Northern Ireland.

heading_context: Replace a lost or damaged MOT certificate
chunks.html_content:
You’ll need:

  • the vehicle registration (number plate)
  • the 11-digit number from the vehicle log book (V5C)
